ca.uqac.lif.labpal

Class ExperimentBuilder<T extends Experiment>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.labpal.ExperimentBuilder<T>

  • public class ExperimentBuilder<T extends Experiment>
extends Object
    Populates the content of an experiment based on results fetched from an external source. This is useful to integrate in a lab results from other experiments (such as results from someone else's paper on the same input data).
    Author:
    Sylvain Hall√©
